        <mxCell id="policy" value="transfer_policy gates everything:&#10;platform_sale | official_only | connect_only | unknown&#10;&#10;Money can only flow for platform_sale - there is no code path&#10;that builds a payment for any other mode. Enforced in the API&#10;service layer and by DB constraints, never only in UI." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#ecfdf5;strokeColor=#047857;fontSize=12;align=left;spacing=8;" vertex="1" parent="1">
